>Office:</strong>Room 217, Building 8</p>\n\n<p><strong>Homepage:</strong>http://sist.shanghaitech.edu.cn/faculty/yuanming</p>\n'),(6208,'<p><strong>Ph.D: </strong>The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology<br>\n<strong>Tel:</strong><br>\n<strong>Email: </strong>shiym@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>Office: </strong>Room 217, Building 8<br>\n<strong>Research Interests:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"white-space: normal;\">\n	<li>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Computational Big Data Analytics:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</b></p>\n	Sparse and Low-Rank Models, Large-Scale Convex and Nonconvex Optimization, Riemannian Optimization, Randomized Sketching</li>\n	<li><b style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\">Mobile Edge/Fog Computing and Networking:</b><br>\n	Caching, Computation Offloading, Privacy, Index Coding</li>\n	<li>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Dense Communication Networking:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</b></p>\n	Cloud-RAN, Fog-RAN, Internet of Things (IoT), Tactile Internet</li>\n</ul>\n'),(6209,'<p><strong>RESEARCHINTERESTS</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"white-space: normal;\">\n \n <li>\n \n <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n \n <b>Computational Big Data Analytics:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</b>\n \n </p>\n \n Sparse and Low-Rank Models, Large-Scale Convex and Nonconvex Optimization, Riemannian Optimization, Randomized Sketching\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n <b style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\">Mobile Edge/Fog Computing and Networking:</b><br>\n \n Caching, Computation Offloading, Privacy, Index Coding<br>\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n \n <b>Dense Communication Networking:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</b>\n \n </p>\n \n Cloud-RAN, Fog-RAN, Internet of Things (IoT), Tactile Internet\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p><strong>BIOGRAPHY</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p>\n \n Dr. Shi received the B.S. degree in electronic engineering from Tsinghua\n \n University, Beijing, China, in 2011. He received the Ph.D. degree in electronic\n \n and computer engineering from The Hong Kong University of Science and\n \n Technology (HKUST), in 2015, under the supervision of Prof. Khaled B. Letaief. Since\n \n September 2015, he has been with the School of Information Science and Technology in ShanghaiTech University, as a tenure-track Assistant\n \n Professor. Dr. Shi received the 2016 Marconi Prize Paper Award in Wireless\n \n Communications.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n His research focuses on massive data analytics, computation, and\n \n communication (MC2) aspects in network science, including computational big\n \n data analytics, information-centric networking, mobile edge/fog computing and\n \n networking, IoT and Tactile Internet, sparse and low-rank models, convex and\n \n nonconvex optimization.\n \n </p><p></p>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p><strong>SELECTEDPUBLICATIONS</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n \n 1. Y. Shi, J. Zhang, and K. B. Letaief, Low-rank matrix completion for\n \n topological interference management by Riemannian pursuit, <i>IEEE Trans. Wireless Commun.</i>, vol. 15,\n \n no. 7, pp. 1-15, Jul. 2016.<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"></span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n \n 2. Y. Shi, J. Cheng, J. Zhang, B. Bai, W. Chen and K. B. Letaief,\n \n Smoothed <i>Lp</i>-minimization for green\n \n Cloud-RAN with user admission control, <i>IEEE\n \n J. Select. Areas Commun.</i>, vol. 34, no. 4, pp. 1-15, Apr. 2016.<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"></span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n \n 3. Y. Shi, J. Zhang, B. ODonoghue, and K. B. Letaief, Large-scale\n \n convex optimization for dense wireless cooperative networks, <i>IEEE Trans. Signal Process</i>., vol. 63,\n \n no. 18, pp. 4729-4743, Sept. 2015.<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"></span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p class=\"MsoNormal\" s